<section xmlns   ="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
         xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
         xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
         xml:id  ="tnt-create"
         version ="5.0">
  <title>Create a Tenant</title>
  <para>
    You can create a new tenants in UID Administration by using the Create Tenant page.
    You can open this page only if you are authorized to create tenants as determined by the authorization policy.
  </para>
  <para>
    To create a tenant:
  </para>
  <orderedlist continuation="restart">
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Click <emphasis role="strong">Tenant</emphasis> in the sidebar menu.
        <mediaobject>
          <alt>Sidebar Tenant</alt>
          <imageobject>
            <!--
             | The location of the image path must be relative to xml:base set
             | at the enclosing book element
             -->
           <imagedata scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%" fileref="src/site/images/en/tnt/sidebar-lg.png" format="PNG"/>
         </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </para>
      <para/>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Click <emphasis role="strong">New</emphasis> on the toolbar.
      </para>
      <para/>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        The Create Tenant page is displayed.
      </para>
      <figure xml:id="tnt-create-fig">
        <title>Create Tenant</title>
        <mediaobject>
          <alt>Create Tenant</alt>
          <imageobject>
            <!--
             | The location of the image path must be relative to xml:base set
             | at the enclosing book element
             -->
           <imagedata scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%" fileref="src/site/images/en/tnt/create.png" format="PNG"/>
         </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </figure>
      <para/>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Enter details of the tyoe in the Create Tenant page.
      </para>
      <para/>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Click <emphasis role="strong">Save</emphasis>.
        A message is displayed stating that the tenant is created successfully.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </orderedlist>
  <table frame="topbot" colsep="0" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="3">
      <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="1*"/>
      <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1*"/>
      <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="2*"/>
      <thead>
        <row>
          <entry>Section</entry>
          <entry>Attribute</entry>
          <entry>Description</entry>
        </row>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry>Basic</entry>
          <entry>Id</entry>
          <entry>A unique identifier of the tenant to create.</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry></entry>
          <entry>Active</entry>
          <entry>The activation status of the tenant to create.</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry></entry>
          <entry>Name</entry>
          <entry>A human readable name of the tenant to create that explains the usage.</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </table>
  <para>
    In the section <emphasis role="strong">Users</emphasis> you can assign users to the tenant and remove users from the tenant.
  </para>
</section>